data.description: Come see the newest swim and tennis community luxury listing! This lovely abode is a 3 sided brick, traditional home conveniently located in the well established city of Conyers. The grand 2 story entrance to this home is amazing! It is followed by a formal living  and dining room. The spacious and open design showcases a beautiful coffered ceiling in the den along side the large kitchen suitable for the best chef. The kitchen boasts immense cabinetry and granite counter space as well as a huge island and a breakfast nook. Upstairs you will find a semi private loft, perfect for a media room or the coveted man cave. The oversized master bedroom and bath has a deep soaking tub with a sizable separate shower and ample closet space. All secondary bedrooms are plentiful in size to accommodate your family, including the guest bedroom and full bath on entry level. AS AN ADDED BONUS, ALL FURNITURE IN HOME IS NEGOTIABLE. Make your appointment today and dont miss out on this immaculate dream home!
